queries.sql: SELECT p.*, o.order_number, c.name, c.profile_picture, o.user_id FROM payments p JOIN orders o ON o.id = p.order_id JOIN users c ON c.id = o.user_id WHERE p.payment_status = '1' LIMIT 5
